  "description": "A Reskin mod of the Half Life Alyx combine NPC mod by Mathias: https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2812691517. The voice lines are from Counter Strike: Condition Zero-Deleted Scenes. Includes US, Russian, French, British, German soldiers as well as Mercaneries, Insurgents, and Cartel Henchmen. Made them less fat. Made 3 variants of each NPC type: Ally, Hostile, and Switchable. Pressing X can toggle the Switchable NPC-s between passive and hostile behaviour. Also made the models more detailed, as well as their weapons. Cheers.",
